<subSubSection type="biology_ecology">
<paragraph pageNumber="38">
Biology. The taxonomy and biology of 
<taxonomicName LSID-HNS="urn:lsid:biosci.ohio-state.edu:osuc_concepts:26005" class="Insecta" family="Formicidae" genus="Azteca" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName-HNS="Azteca longiceps Emery" order="Hymenoptera" pageNumber="38" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="longiceps">A. longiceps</taxonomicName>
was reviewed in Longino (1996). 
<taxonomicName LSID-HNS="urn:lsid:biosci.ohio-state.edu:osuc_concepts:26005" class="Insecta" family="Formicidae" genus="Azteca" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName-HNS="Azteca longiceps Emery" order="Hymenoptera" pageNumber="38" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="longiceps">Azteca longiceps</taxonomicName>
is an obligate inhabitant of myrmecophytic 
<taxonomicName class="Magnoliopsida" family="Polygonaceae" genus="Triplaris" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Plantae" order="Caryophyllales" pageNumber="38" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="genus">Triplaris</taxonomicName>
trees.
</paragraph>
